Examples:
  .claude/tools/webref heading html 4.13                     # all §4.13.x sections
  .claude/tools/webref heading ecma262 25.5.2                # §25.5.2 JSON.parse
  .claude/tools/webref aoid ecma262 ToNumber                 # AO → §7.1.4 + anchor
